<div class='helpcontent'>
A <b>bundle</b> <a href='#' class='chelp bundle'>?</a> is a resource that groups a selected set of substances and a selected set of endpoints. 
<br/>
The nanomaterials <a href='#' class='chelp nanomaterial'>?</a> are considered a special case of substances <a href='#' class='chelp substance'>?</a>.
See <a href="http://www.beilstein-journals.org/bjnano/single/articleFullText.htm?publicId=2190-4286-6-165#F9" target=_blank>doi:10.3762/bjnano.6.165</a>.

